cursor.description: A token used to return the next page of a previous request. Use the cursor provided in the previous response.

started_after.description:
Only includes calls that started more recently than the specified timestamp.
(UTC ms-since-epoch timestamp)

started_before.description:
Only includes calls that started prior to the specified timestamp.
(UTC ms-since-epoch timestamp)

target_id.description: The ID of a target to filter against.

target_type.description: The target type associated with the target ID.
